title: 'Not bad'
body: The product has value for money. However the contents seems like little bit old. As shown in photos, the measuring tape's tag clip seems to start rusting. In the case of hammer, the metallic ring was supposed to be attached to the head, but instead it's loose and will move back and forth whenever the hammer is even lifted/tilted

title: 'Feels Premium. A Must Have Tool if you need to manage few things by your own in home.'
body: 'In this package you get all the robust tools. From the plier to the Inch tape the build quality of every tool is great. The hammer is tough. The holding grip of every tool is strong smooth and comfortable to hold. Feels premium.  Pros: Feels Premium A great Build quality Robust & Rigid Grip is smooth & comfortable'
